CORPUS PROVENANCE STATEMENT

The image corpus consists of researcher-constructed phishing lookalike
pages. Adversarial URL modifications are drawn from attack taxonomies
observed in real-world threat intelligence work. The corpus was
finalized before any model was tested and not modified during
benchmarking.

The corpus is intended for use in AI safety research, security tool
evaluation, and academic study of vision-language model behavior under
adversarial conditions. Users redistributing the corpus should preserve
this provenance statement.
